text: (yakub nabi, yusuf nabita) “mage adaraniya putune! oba dutu sihinaya obage sahodarayinta nopavasanu. (ese pævasuvahot) ovun obata vipatak kirimata kumantrana karanu æta. mandayat niyata vasayenma seyitan minisunta prakata satureku vasayen sitinneya. (kumantrana karana men ovunva mohu polambavannata ida æta)” yayi pævasuveya
